data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET- PRICE REDUCTION- MOTIVATED SELLER!  Come to sunny Florida and enjoy this 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home with mother-in-law suite. The mother-in-law suite has a separate entrance and parking, with a carport. This home has two driveways, with a carport on one driveway. The main kitchen has LUX vinyl flooring and a dishwasher, stove, and refrigerator. The cabinets are updated. The dishwasher is new 2023. There is also a large laundry room adjacent to the kitchen, with a washer/dryer and room for a desk or table. The refrigerator is in this room. The dining room extends beyond the kitchen. The main living room has water resistant Luxury Vinyl flooring and a ceiling fan. The home interior has been recently painted throughout. The main bedroom has Luxury vinyl flooring and a ceiling fan. The guest room has LUX Vinyl flooring, with a ceiling fan as well. The main bathroom has a tub/shower and single sink vanity. The mother-in-law suite has laminate flooring in the living room and bonus space. The bonus space was used as a bedroom but would make a great office or nursery also. The main bedroom currently has carpet. Laminate flooring has been purchased. There is a large all new custom closet/dresser. There is a washer/dryer and kitchen table off the bedroom. The kitchen has all new custom cabinets, Corian countertops, a dishwasher, refrigerator, and stove. The roof and central air conditioning are new as of 2020. This home has a large backyard with double gates which could be used to park your RV or boat. There is also a fire pit. There are no deed restrictions or HOA in this neighborhood.
